snippet.title: Beer City Board Games
snippet.description:
Beer City Board Games: Brewed for Fun, Best Served Strategically.

Welcome to Beer City Board Games, a community-focused channel where we celebrate all things board gaming. From classic favorites to modern masterpieces, we explore the world of tabletop games and share our love for this hobby.

At the heart of our channel is a commitment to making board gaming accessible to everyone. We believe that anyone can enjoy board games, regardless of their experience level, age, or background. Whether you're a seasoned veteran or a newcomer to the hobby, we hope you feel welcome here.

So if you're looking for a channel that's all about celebrating the joys of board gaming and building connections with others, subscribe to our channel today. And don't forget to follow us on Instagram and Facebook for even more board game content and community!

snippet.title: Tabletop Tastings
snippet.description:
Tabletop Tastings is the perfect pairing of board games and whisky!

Once a month we reveal a new board game, do a full teach and playthrough, and select the perfect whisky to pair with the experience!  These videos are close to an hour or more and can be found in our "Playthrough & Pairing" playlists.

On a weekly basis, we do a "Sip & Play".  These are where we do a broad overview of a newer or classic board game and recommend a whisky to enjoy with your next playthrough of the game.  Episodes are shorter and a fun way to learn about both board games and whisky!

snippet.title: I TEACH HER SHE WINS
snippet.description:
üé≤ Welcome to I Teach Her She Wins ‚Äì a hilarious international board game web series where strategy meets comedy and the teacher always loses! Based between Italy and the US, our episodes are in English (with a touch of accent flair üòâ) and feature the best card and board games‚Äîfrom quick tutorials and game reviews to winning strategies and fun facts.
Each video includes:
üé≠ A short comedy sketch with actors from both countries
üì¶ Unboxings, rules explanations, and how to win tips
üòÇ Plenty of bloopers, laughs, and surprises

Whether you're a casual gamer or a tabletop enthusiast, our goal is simple: to make you laugh, learn, and fall in love with board games all over again.

üëâ Support us and explore more at: https://albertoresti.com/i-teach-her-she-wins/

snippet.title: Learn to Play Games
snippet.description:
We make videos about one of the things we love‚Ä¶GAMES!  We play a lot of games. Game nights, game conventions, demoing games‚Ä¶ we're continually learning new ones. So, what happens when we go back to a game that we haven‚Äôt played for a while?!?! We forgot some of the rules and how to play‚Ä¶Bummer! 

We have to learn the rules and understand the gameplay for every game that ends up in our hands. We‚Äôve already done the hard part here at Learn To Play Games, so let us give you the quick and easy way to learn the game without skimping out on the finer points. It's all about minimizing the time you have to spend figuring it out and maximizing your time to play so that you can quickly ‚ÄúRoll the dice, and dive in‚Äù!

snippet.title: Rolling Dice & Taking Names
snippet.description:
Rolling Dice & Taking Names is a show where two long time friends discuss the board game hobby including reviews, previews and interviews. The goal is to be entertaining while trying to be informative. Many discussions lead to squirrel moments where we end up discussing food, pop culture and even lawn equipment. 

The main show is a bi-weekly podcast with occasional videos.
